V 0.5.0 - 2023-02-02

* Add dragable icons / buttons to right sidebar
* Add dragable icons / buttons to tiddler info area
* improve icon and link tooltips and aria labels
* Allow the standard bundles to preview the list in AdvancedSearch

V 0.4.4 - 2023-01-18

* Fix ViewTemplate for tiddlers tagged $:/tags/Filter to show text-field
* Add more documentation to the edition
* Add several screenshots to the docs


V 0.4.3 - 2023-01-03

* Fix [[ bundler: auto-renamed tiddlers have wrong date #121|https://github.com/wikilabs/plugins/issues/121]]
* Add new ViewTemplate cascade option for tiddlers tagged: `$:/tags/Filter`
** This template shows the `description` and the `filter` fields
** Also works for core filter infos

V 0.4.2 - 2022-03-31

* Fix import viewtemplate cascade
* Temporarily use core default import dialogue, till filter can be improved

V 0.4.2 - 2022-03-25

* ''Important'': Changed license to Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike -- [[CC-BY-NC-SA|$:/plugins/wikilabs/bundler/license]]
* Some plugin configurations are enabled now, for convenience
* Add new upgrader to rename images comming from the clipboard
** Add new settings to $:/ControlPanel
* Add seconds to $:/config/wikilabs/bundler/importHeaderTemplate

V 0.4.1 - 2021-10-07

* fix newline character

V 0.4.0 - 2021-10-06

* "New Bundle" button uses $:/StoryList list-field to seed the text field
* ''Important:''
** $:/core/ui/ImportListing is  ''not overwritten'' anymore
** [[$:/core/modules/upgraders/system.js]] is ''not overwritten'' anymore

V 0.3.2 - 2021-03-16

* Fix history tiddler version
* Fix Import edit name element

V 0.3.1 - 2021-02-23

* ''Important:'' The plugin overwrites [[$:/core/modules/upgraders/system.js]] now

* Add a new tab to the tiddler (i)nfo area
** The "Bundle" tab contains a "list", "export" and "open in ~AdvancedSearch" buttons

* Improve configuration panel
** We have all important settings on 1 page now
** The config panel can be reached from the "bundles" tab in the sidebar

* Make `prefix[--- ]]` the standard for tiddler titles, that are used as comments
** It's easy to read and we didn't get complains for 2 years, since the suggestion was made

* $:/StoryList*, $:/HistoryList*, "$:/state/*" and "$:/temp/*" are importable now
** This will allow us to work with multiple stories

* We use `subfilter` instead of `enlist` now
** This unifies simple-list and filtered-list handling

* Add a plugin icon {{$:/plugins/wikilabs/bundler/icon}}

* Slightly improved docs ;) [[Tips and Tricks]]

* Known Issues!
** System tiddlers are always selected atm. This will change in the future, but we need core support here!

V 0.1.3 - 2020-12-25

* update license

V 0.1.2 - 2020.01.19

* Update license link/text

V 0.1.1 - beta 2017.06.18

* improve license links and readme
* fix upgrade.js title

V 0.1.0 - beta

* new name: bundler
* this name change makes it incompatible to older settings!

** new "Enable Overwrite Check" option. default = no

V 0.0.1 - beta

* initial release
* name: bundles
