* Documentation and more can be found at: https://wikilabs.github.io/editions/bundler
* The position of the "Bundles" tab can be selected in the <$button actions=<<openControlBundlesTab>> class="tc-btn-invisible tc-tiddlylink">~$:/ControlPanel : Bundles tab</$button>
